snippet.title: Diana and Roma show School rules / New Back to School story
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma show the School Rules: what to wear to school, what to put in your backpack, what kind of lunch box to take and how to behave at school. New Back to School story from Diana and Roma.
Thanks for watching!
